PN,42208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1781394469
OL,3,CMan lost eye in Belfast knife attack,
OL,4,Ccourt told as suspect appears before
OL,5,Cjudge
OL,7,FPoliticians and journalists have been
OL,8,Fthreatened. The Lord Mayor of Belfast
OL,9,Fsaid she has received death threats,
OL,10,Fsaying they will not deter her from
OL,11,Fher work.
OL,13,FSinn Fein's Rois-Maire Donnelly said
OL,14,Fthe threats "will not deter" her from
OL,15,Ffulfilling her duties as she called
OL,16,Ffor the people of Belfast to reject
OL,17,Fracism and "stand with" immigrants who
OL,18,Fhave become "valued members of our
OL,19,Fcommunity".
OL,21,FTwo police officers were injured.
OL,26,@uD@GrruD@NrwuD@SrpvD@MOUvD@\O]yD@LOUyD@
OL,26,AWO]zD@MOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
