PN,42213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1781394469
OL,3,CMan lost eye in Belfast knife attack,
OL,4,Ccourt told as suspect appears before
OL,5,Cjudge
OL,7,FPublic transport operator Translink
OL,8,Fsaid bus services will stop at 5pm and
OL,9,Fthere will be no train services
OL,10,Fdeparting after 6pm due to expected
OL,11,Fprotests on Wednesday.
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland's Education Authority
OL,14,Fsaid schools should take individual
OL,15,Fdecisions on whether to close. A
OL,16,Fnumber of schools had already taken
OL,17,Fthe decision to close by noon on
OL,18,FWednesday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
