PN,42214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1781394469
OL,3,CMan lost eye in Belfast knife attack,
OL,4,Ccourt told as suspect appears before
OL,5,Cjudge
OL,7,FIn a statement, the authority said:
OL,8,F"EA is grateful to all schools and
OL,9,Fyouth organisations for their support
OL,10,Fto children and young people at this
OL,11,Ftime.
OL,13,F"We are all agreed maintaining the
OL,14,Feducation of children and young people
OL,15,Fis a vital priority.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/16
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,423,410,140,120,000,100
PN,42215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1781394469
OL,3,CMan lost eye in Belfast knife attack,
OL,4,Ccourt told as suspect appears before
OL,5,Cjudge
OL,7,F"In that context, while we are aware
OL,8,Fof unverified social media claims
OL,9,Fabout further planned protests today,
OL,10,Fa blanket decision regarding closures
OL,11,Ffor the whole of NI would be neither
OL,12,Fpractical nor proportionate.
OL,14,F"Individual school leaders should
OL,15,Fcontinue to closely monitor the
OL,16,Fsituation in their local area, and the
OL,17,Fcommuting pathway for staff and
OL,18,Fpupils, and react as necessary and
OL,19,Fappropriate.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/16
